<plot>'Little Houses' is a short documentary about the burial customs of a small Louisiana community. In Mermentau Cove, Louisiana - Acadian settlers buried their dead in small wooden houses. Today, only three of those houses remain. 'Little Houses' is the story of three remaining monuments and their path to preservation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?338132</url></doc>
